                        KASIT, established in 2000 under the directives of His Majesty King Abdullah II, aims to develop IT in Jordan. The faculty offers accredited programs in Computer Science, Computer Information Systems, and Business Information Technology, aligned with ABET standards.
                    </p>
                </div>
                <div class="col-md-1 col-lg-1 col-xl-1 d-flex justify-content-end">
                    <div class="vertical-line"></div>
                </div>

                <div class="col-md-2 col-lg-2 col-xl-2   justify-content-start align-text-top">
                    <div class="footer-item d-flex flex-column">
                        <a href="/Home/Index" class="ahref"> Home</a>
                        <a href="/Home/UpcomingEvents" class="ahref"> Upcoming Events</a>
                        <a href="/Home/Archive" class="ahref"> Archive</a>
                        <a href="/Home/FAQ" class="ahref"> FAQ</a>
                    </div>
                </div>

                <div class="col-md-1 col-lg-1 col-xl-1 d-flex justify-content-end">
                    <div class="vertical-line"></div>
                </div>

                <div class="col-md-3 col-lg-3 col-xl-3">
                    <div class="footer-item d-flex flex-column">
                        <h4 class="text-white">Contact Us</h4>
                        <a href="tel:+962 6 5355 000" class="ahref"> +962 6 5355 000</a>
                        <a href="mailto:kasit@ju.edu.jo" class="ahref"> kasit@ju.edu.jo</a>
                        <br />
                        <div class="d-flex align-items-center">
                            <a class="rounded-pill icon-circle mx-1" href="https://www.facebook.com/KASIT.Official">
                                <i class="fa-brands fa-facebook-f fa-xl" style="color: #08436A;"></i>
                            </a>
                            <a class="rounded-pill icon-circle mx-1" href="https://www.instagram.com/kasit.official/">
                                <i class="fa-brands fa-instagram fa-xl" style="color: #08436A;"></i>
                            </a>
                            <a class="rounded-pill icon-circle mx-1" href="https://www.linkedin.com/in/kasit-ju-575452241/">
